T1  - Polycystic Ovary Syndrome: A Contemporary Clinical Approach.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.2174/1381612827666210119104721
A1  - Bjekic-Macut, Jelica
A1  - Vukasin, Tamara
A1  - Velija-Asimi, Zelija
A1  - Burekovic, Azra
