T1  - Experts' opinion on inositols in treating polycystic ovary syndrome and non-insulin dependent diabetes mellitus: a further help for human reproduction and beyond.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1080/17425255.2020.1737675
A1  - Facchinetti, Fabio
A1  - Appetecchia, Marialuisa
A1  - Aragona, Cesare
A1  - Bevilacqua, Arturo
